    <title>SSH免密码登陆服务器</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/08/30/SSH%E5%85%8D%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E7%99%BB%E9%99%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/08/30/SSH免密码登陆服务器/</id>
    <published>2017-08-30T06:54:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-08-31T08:41:19.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://share.alihanniba.com/mac/2017-08-11-024936.jpg" alt=""></p>
<blockquote>
<p>题图：Pixabay</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="1-下载SSH"><a href="#1-下载SSH" class="headerlink" title="1.下载SSH"></a>1.下载SSH</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">//mac</div><div class="line">brew install ssh</div><div class="line">//ubuntu</div><div class="line">apt-get install ssh</div><div class="line">//centos</div><div class="line">yun install ssh</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="2-生成SSH密匙与公匙"><a href="#2-生成SSH密匙与公匙" class="headerlink" title="2.生成SSH密匙与公匙"></a>2.生成SSH密匙与公匙</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://share.alihanniba.com/mac/2017-08-11-025126.jpg" alt=""><br>默认全部回车，之后进入默认文件夹，默认生成的是密匙id_rsa、公匙id_rsa.pub。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">cd ~/.ssh &amp;&amp; ls</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://share.alihanniba.com/mac/2017-08-11-025153.jpg" alt=""></p>
<h4 id="3-将公匙上传至服务器"><a href="#3-将公匙上传至服务器" class="headerlink" title="3.将公匙上传至服务器"></a>3.将公匙上传至服务器</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ssh-copy-id root@alihanniba.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此处我的已经上传过了。上传过程中需要输入服务器密码<br><img src="https://share.alihanniba.com/mac/2017-08-11-025221.jpg" alt=""><br>当服务器没有.ssh文件时，需先新建一个</p>
<h4 id="4-设置SSH登陆别名"><a href="#4-设置SSH登陆别名" class="headerlink" title="4.设置SSH登陆别名"></a>4.设置SSH登陆别名</h4><p>打开SSH配置文件，没有就新建一个</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">vim ~/.ssh/config</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>输入</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Host alihanniba.com				# 自定义别名</div><div class="line">  HostName alihanniba.com		# ssh服务器ip或domain</div><div class="line">  Port 22							# ssh服务器端口，默认为22</div><div class="line">  User root							# ssh服务器用户名</div><div class="line">  PreferredAuthentications publickey</div><div class="line">  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa			# 公钥文件对应的私钥文件</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="5-快捷登陆"><a href="#5-快捷登陆" class="headerlink" title="5.快捷登陆"></a>5.快捷登陆</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ssh alihanniba.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://share.alihanniba.com/mac/2017-08-11-025249.jpg" alt=""></p>]]></content>
    
